games.comment: Marques Colston fantasy owners, send your hate mail to Reggie Bush. Bush led the game in receptions with 8 for 112 yards and a touchdown. Colston collected just 3 catches for 26 yards.    Despite everything I just said, the Buccaneers still had a shot to win, as they traveled into Saints territory as time was winding down. Garcia just couldn't get the job done, throwing a pick to

Marques Colston caught 2 touchdown passes. Colston, who has been quiet most of the season, finished with 6 receptions. But don't go grabbing Colston for your fantasy team. He finished with only 36 receiving yards, and his 2 touchdowns were a case of being in the right place at the right time.
